---
title: Parmigiana-Style Eggplant & Pangrattato with Spiced Fries & Plant-Based Mayo
description: Yes, you can whip up an eggplant parmie at home – it’s not that hard! At least our version isn’t – with hearty eggplant steaks that
are lightly roasted, then baked to get a golden tomato and crumb topping. Served with a pear salad and hearty fries, this
shows you can always improve on the classics!
